title: Share of the population who gave to charity in England 2019 , by age
summary: In general Share of respondents has rose over the Year.
Share of respondents is slightly increasing from 25_to_34 to 35_to_49.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 25_to_34 and 35_to_49.
The highest Share of respondents, of value 76.0 was reached at Year 35_to_49
The lowest Share of respondents, of value 69.0 was reported at Year 25_to_34
